metadata.name: MXM
metadata.description:
MXM is MixMob’s governance token on Solana that operates the MXM Esports League  and incentivizes players. MXM holders get three main benefits:

ACCESS & ELIGIBILITY
Players can earn MXM tokens from the MixMob reward pools.

REFERRAL REWARDS
Players who refer other new players to their Arenas (or generally to the game) would be able to receive SUD$ & MXM.

GOVERNANCE
Shape the future and rules of the MXM League, Turbo Arena and Crews. MXM token puts power in players’ hands – your game, your rules.
